  <!-- Author(s) Bio -->

  <section class="po-fr__bio">
    <h1 class="po-fr__heading">About the Author</h1>
    
      <p class="po-fr__desc">Bernd Gehrke was raised in East Berlin and was a member of East Germany’s left opposition, co-founding the United Left and the Green League in 1989. In 2013 he edited the anthology <cite><a href="http://www.unrast-verlag.de/gesamtprogramm/allgemeines-programm/politik-gesellschaft/was-tun-mit-kommunismus-399-detail">Was tun mit Kommunismus?!</a></cite> with Anne Seeck and Ralf Landmesser.</p>
    

    
    
      
    

    
    
      
    
